Mechel Steelmaking Unit May Borrow $304 Million From Sberbank

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-07-21T08:30:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/mechel-steelmaking-unit-may-borrow-304-million-from-sberbank.html
OAO  Mechel (MTL) ’s steelmaking unit agreed
with OAO Sberbank to borrow as much as 8.5 billion rubles ($304
million) in two equally split credit lines, a regulatory filing
shows.  The board of the unit,  Chelyabinsk Metallurgical Plant (CHMK) ,
approved the deal today.  Mechel (MTLR) ’s total debt as of March 31 was $8.2 billion,
filings show.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
